%% Authored stress fixture (Mermaid@11.12.2): fork/join + choice routing.

[*] --> Fork

state Fork <<fork>>
Fork --> Load
Fork --> Prepare

Load --> Decide
Prepare --> Decide

state Decide <<choice>>
Decide -->|ok| Join
Decide -->|retry| Load
Decide -->|fail| Abort

state Join <<join>>
Join --> Done

Abort --> [*]
Done --> [*]
